fields.value: Weighted Tardiness Scheduling with Sequence-Dependent Setups: A Benchmark Library

dsDescriptionValue.value: This set of benchmark instances for the problem known as Weighted Tardiness Scheduling with Sequence Dependent Setups originated in 2003 as part of the Ph.D. Dissertation research of Vincent A. Cicirello from Carnegie Mellon University's Robotics Institute. See https://www.cicirello.org/datasets/wtsds/ for more information about the dataset including relevant publications.
